{"tid":2381081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.31 半周年非法集結案　警認被告無暴力行為　僅「向我哋講粗口」","createTime":"2021-01-26T10:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T12:44:49.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9a6a4e2df450935a3c1d7a2f667bcbde3e5abe","tid":2381081,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"去年 8.31 太子事件半周年，旺角一帶爆發衝突。36 歲男子被指衝向警方防線，大叫「X 你老母死黑警」，否認非法集結罪，今（26 日）在西九龍裁判法院受審。督察邢展豪承認當時無人衝擊警方，示威者僅站在馬路上叫囂。他指現場仍有其他路人，涉案男子沒有暴力行為，形容他「邊行邊鬧」。刑又指當時觀察該男子 10 多秒，控方問他能否在庭上認出涉案男子，<span class=\"red\">刑未能認出，稱「單靠長相未必認到」。</span><br />\n<br />\n刑續指，被告沒有攜帶可疑物品，亦沒有暴力行為，形容他「邊行邊鬧」，向警員講粗口。辯方指被告其實有戴口罩，<span class=\"red\">刑改稱「可能我記錯」；辯方又指刑在口供沒有提及被告講粗口一事，刑同意。</span>"},{"pid":"dadc75f253d9626d064e4dc0c47a156a2eb71cd2","tid":2381081,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-31-%E5%8D%8A%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E6%A1%88-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%84%A1%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E5%83%85-%E5%90%91%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E8%AC%9B%E7%B2%97%E5%8F%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-31-%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E5%2583%2585-%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E8%25AC%259B%25E7%25B2%2597%25E5%258F%25A3%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSvw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=1ff59874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-31-%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%259A%2